<div style="text-align: center">
</div>
<br>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-2" id="leftfixed">
       <div class="affix" style="margin-left: -80px;">
         <img style="" src="https://d30y9cdsu7xlg0.cloudfront.net/png/3878-200.png"/>
         <div style="margin-left:-130px" class="mycontent-left">
           {{new-comment saveAnswer="saveAnswer" discussion=model}}
       </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-10">
      <div class="mycontent-right-discussion">
        <ul style="list-style: none;">
          <h1> Discussion for: {{model.name}} </h1>
      <h3>Discussion points:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Was it useful for you?</li>
    <li>At what point in the curriculum did you find it most helpful?</li>
    <li>Was it easy to digest</li>
    <li>What type of learner would benefit from this material?</li>
  </ul>
  <hr>
      {{#each model.discussions as |discussion|}}
        <li><span style="font-weight: bold;">{{discussion.author}} says:</span> {{discussion.comment}}</li>
        <br>

      {{/each}}
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
</div>


